    "udt_struct_v0": {
      "doc": "One step in a custodial route. Like an Instruction but with two extra knobs\\nthe custodial path needs:\\n- `auth_declarations`: what the router pre-authorizes for this step (see above)\\n- `output_token`: hint for downstream balance reads / fee bases (optional)",
