          "type_": "symbol"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "udt_struct_v0": {
      "doc": "A fee taken from a token the router holds, mid-route.\\n`after_instruction = i` means \"right after `steps[i]` returns, take `bps`\\nof the router's current balance of `token` and split among `affiliates`.\"",
      "lib": "",
      "name": "IntermediateFee",
